name: Guymere 2
overview: Presented before you is a string of Lemmings, click the button and they fart in the face of the one behind them. This game was the 1994 equivalent of being Rickrolled. You spent time downloading this game and in the end got a face full of stink. Then, because you needed to keep your upload\download ratio up, you shared it and passed on the stink to someone else. There were several sequels to this game.
